<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>אידית קליימן - קוד פתוח | סדנה</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Heebo:wght@300;400;500;700;800&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@1,400;1,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --bg:#0A0A0A;--bg2:#111111;--bg3:#161616;--card:#141414;
  --text:#FFFFFF;--t2:#CCCCCC;--t3:#888888;
  --gold:#C8A96A;--gld2:#DFC080;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'Heebo',sans-serif;overflow-x:hidden;direction:rtl;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}

nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;padding:1.4rem 6vw;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;background:rgba(10,10,10,0.95);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05)}
.nav-logo{width:95px}
.nav-btn{font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:600;color:#0A0A0A;background:var(--gold);padding:0.65rem 1.8rem;text-decoration:none;transition:background 0.25s}
.nav-btn:hover{background:var(--gld2)}

#hero{position:relative;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;overflow:hidden}
.hero-img{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 20%;opacity:0.55;filter:grayscale(100%) brightness(0.85)}
.hero-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(10,10,10,0.1) 0%,rgba(10,10,10,0.0) 20%,rgba(10,10,10,0.5) 60%,rgba(10,10,10,0.97) 100%)}
.hero-content{position:relative;z-index:2;width:100%;padding:0 6vw 8rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;margin-top:auto}
.hero-logo-img{display:none}
.hero-h1{font-size:clamp(2.4rem,6vw,5.5rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.15;color:var(--text);text-align:right;margin-bottom:1.5rem;opacity:0;animation:up 1s ease 0.45s forwards}
.hero-h1 span{color:var(--gold)}
.hero-sub{font-size:clamp(1rem,1.8vw,1.25rem);font-weight:300;color:var(--t2);text-align:right;max-width:520px;margin-bottom:1.5rem;opacity:0;animation:up 1s ease 0.65s forwards;line-height:1.8}
.hero-details{display:flex;gap:2rem;margin-bottom:3rem;opacity:0;animation:up 1s ease 0.75s forwards}
.hero-detail{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end}
.hero-detail-label{font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--t3)}
.hero-detail-val{font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gold)}
.btn-gold{display:inline-block;background:var(--gold);color:#0A0A0A;padding:1.1rem 3.5rem;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.25s;opacity:0;animation:up 1s ease 0.85s forwards}
.btn-gold:hover{background:var(--gld2);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.btn-outline{display:inline-block;border:2px solid var(--gold);color:var(--gold);padding:1.1rem 3.5rem;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.25s;background:transparent}
.btn-outline:hover{background:var(--gold);color:#0A0A0A}

#opener{background:var(--bg2);padding:8rem 6vw;text-align:center}
.opener-inner{max-width:740px;margin:0 auto}
.opener-pre{font-size:clamp(1.05rem,1.8vw,1.3rem);font-weight:300;color:var(--t3);line-height:2.2;margin-bottom:3rem}
.opener-main{font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.8rem);font-weight:700;line-height:1.4;color:var(--text)}
.opener-main span{color:var(--gold)}
.opener-sub{font-size:clamp(1rem,1.6vw,1.2rem);font-weight:300;color:var(--t2);margin-top:2rem;line-height:1.9}

#pain{background:var(--bg3);padding:8rem 6vw}
.pain-inner{max-width:1060px;margin:0 auto}
.pain-header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:4rem}
.sec-label{font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.4em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:1.5rem;display:block}
.sec-h2{font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;color:var(--text)}
.sec-h2 span{color:var(--gold)}
.pain-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:1.2rem}
.pain-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border-right:3px solid var(--gold);padding:2.2rem 2rem;transition:transform 0.3s}
.pain-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px)}
.pain-card-title{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:0.8rem}
.pain-card-body{font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--t2);line-height:1.85}

#workshop{background:var(--bg);padding:9rem 6vw}
.workshop-inner{max-width:1060px;margin:0 auto}
.workshop-header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:5rem}
.workshop-header .sec-h2{margin-top:1rem}
.workshop-header p{font-size:clamp(1rem,1.6vw,1.15rem);font-weight:300;color:var(--t2);margin-top:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;max-width:600px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}
.steps-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;max-width:720px;margin:0 auto}
.step-item{display:flex;gap:2rem;padding:2.4rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);align-items:flex-start}
.step-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.step-num{font-size:2.8rem;font-weight:800;color:rgba(200,169,106,0.3);line-height:1;min-width:48px}
.step-body{flex:1}
.step-title{font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:0.7rem;line-height:1.3}
.step-desc{font-size:0.97rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--t2);line-height:1.85}

#about{background:var(--bg2);padding:8rem 6vw}
.about-grid{max-width:1060px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:center}
.about-img-wrap{position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.about-img{width:100%;display:block;filter:grayscale(20%) contrast(1.05);transition:transform 0.6s ease}
.about-img-wrap:hover .about-img{transform:scale(1.02)}
.about-img-wrap::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(10,10,10,0.5) 0%,transparent 50%)}
.about-right{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0}
.about-h2{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,3rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:2.5rem}
.about-h2 span{color:var(--gold)}
.fact-block{background:var(--card);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border-right:3px solid var(--gold);padding:1.6rem 1.8rem;margin-bottom:1.2rem}
.fact-block p{font-size:clamp(0.95rem,1.5vw,1.05rem);font-weight:300;color:var(--t2);line-height:1.85}
.fact-block strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:500}
.about-quote{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(1.5rem,2.5vw,2.2rem);font-style:italic;color:var(--gold);line-height:1.5;margin-top:2rem;border-right:3px solid var(--gold);padding-right:1.5rem}

#notteaching{background:var(--bg3);padding:9rem 6vw;text-align:center}
.not-inner{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto}
.not-items{margin-bottom:4rem}
.not-item{font-size:clamp(1.2rem,2.2vw,1.8rem);font-weight:300;color:var(--t3);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:1rem;text-decoration:line-through;text-decoration-color:rgba(200,169,106,0.25)}
.not-divider{width:2px;height:60px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent,var(--gold),transparent);margin:0 auto 4rem;opacity:0.5}
.yes-main{font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5.5vw,5rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.15;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.yes-main span{color:var(--gold)}
.yes-sub{font-size:clamp(1rem,1.6vw,1.2rem);font-weight:300;color:var(--t2);line-height:1.9}

/* REGISTER SECTION */
#register{background:var(--bg);padding:9rem 6vw;text-align:center}
.register-inner{max-width:780px;margin:0 auto}
.register-eyebrow{font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.4em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:2rem;display:block}
.register-h2{font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5vw,4rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.15;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:1rem}
.register-h2 span{color:var(--gold)}
.register-sub{font-size:clamp(1rem,1.6vw,1.15rem);font-weight:300;color:var(--t2);margin-bottom:4rem;line-height:1.9}
.register-details{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);margin-bottom:4rem}
.register-detail{background:var(--card);padding:2.5rem 1.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.4rem}
.rd-icon{font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:0.2rem}
.rd-label{font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--t3)}
.rd-value{font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);line-height:1.35;text-align:center}
.rd-note{font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--t3);text-align:center}
.register-price-wrap{margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.register-price{font-size:clamp(4rem,9vw,7rem);font-weight:800;color:var(--gold);line-height:1}
.register-price sup{font-size:0.35em;font-weight:300;color:var(--t2);vertical-align:top;margin-top:0.5em}
.register-price-note{font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--t3);margin-top:0.5rem}
.spots-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0A0A0A;background:var(--gold);padding:5px 18px;margin-bottom:3rem}

.reg-form{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;max-width:460px;margin:0 auto 1rem}
.reg-form input{background:var(--bg3);border:none;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(200,169,106,0.3);padding:1.1rem 1rem;font-size:1rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--text);font-family:'Heebo',sans-serif;outline:none;transition:border-color 0.25s;text-align:right;width:100%}
.reg-form input::placeholder{color:var(--t3)}
.reg-form input:focus{border-bottom-color:var(--gold)}
.btn-register{display:block;width:100%;background:var(--gold);color:#0A0A0A;padding:1.4rem 3.5rem;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.06em;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Heebo',sans-serif;transition:all 0.25s;margin-top:0.5rem}
.btn-register:hover{background:var(--gld2);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.privacy-note{font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--t3);margin-top:0.5rem}
.success-msg{display:none;background:rgba(200,169,106,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(200,169,106,0.25);padding:2.5rem;font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--gold);font-weight:500;max-width:460px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.7}

/* CTA */
#cta{background:var(--bg);padding:0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;min-height:70vh;align-items:stretch}
.cta-img-wrap{position:relative;overflow:hidden;min-height:500px}
.cta-img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center top;filter:grayscale(30%) brightness(0.75);transition:transform 0.6s ease}
.cta-img-wrap:hover .cta-img{transform:scale(1.02)}
.cta-img-wrap::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to left,rgba(10,10,10,0.7) 0%,transparent 60%)}
.cta-right{background:var(--bg2);padding:6rem 5vw;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}
.cta-hline{width:40px;height:1px;background:var(--gold);opacity:0.4;margin:2rem 0}
.cta-eyebrow{font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.4em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:2rem;display:block}
.cta-h2{font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,3rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.3;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.cta-h2 span{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:400;color:var(--gold);font-size:1.1em}
.cta-sub{font-size:clamp(1rem,1.5vw,1.15rem);font-weight:300;color:var(--t2);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:3rem}

footer{padding:2.5rem 6vw;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;background:var(--bg2)}
.footer-logo{width:95px;opacity:0.45}
.footer-tag{font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--t3);letter-spacing:0.15em}

/* FLOATING BAR */
.float-bar{position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:200;background:rgba(10,10,10,0.97);border-top:1px solid rgba(200,169,106,0.3);padding:1rem 6vw;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;transform:translateY(100%);transition:transform 0.4s ease}
.float-bar.show{transform:translateY(0)}
.float-bar-info{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:2rem}
.float-bar-detail{display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.float-bar-label{font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--t3);margin-bottom:2px}
.float-bar-value{font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text)}
.float-bar-price{font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--gold)}
.float-bar-sep{width:1px;height:36px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}

.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);transition:opacity 0.75s ease,transform 0.75s ease}
.reveal.on{opacity:1;transform:none}
@keyframes up{to{opacity:1;transform:none}}

@media(max-width:780px){
  /* NAV */
  nav{padding:1rem 5vw}
  .nav-logo{width:75px}
  .nav-btn{padding:0.55rem 1.2rem;font-size:0.8rem}

  /* HERO */
  #hero{min-height:100svh}
  .hero-content{padding:0 5vw 5rem;align-items:flex-start}
  .hero-h1{font-size:2.2rem;text-align:right}
  .hero-sub{font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:1.2rem}
  .hero-details{gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .hero-detail-val{font-size:0.85rem}
  .btn-gold{padding:0.95rem 2.2rem;font-size:0.95rem}

  /* OPENER */
  #opener{padding:5rem 5vw}
  .opener-pre{font-size:0.95rem;line-height:2}
  .opener-main{font-size:1.4rem;line-height:1.5}
  .opener-sub{font-size:0.92rem}

  /* PAIN */
  #pain{padding:5rem 5vw}
  .pain-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .pain-card{padding:1.6rem 1.4rem}

  /* WORKSHOP */
  #workshop{padding:5rem 5vw}
  .workshop-header{margin-bottom:3rem}
  .step-item{gap:1rem;padding:1.6rem 0}
  .step-num{font-size:2rem;min-width:36px}
  .step-title{font-size:1rem}
  .step-desc{font-size:0.88rem}

  /* ABOUT */
  #about{padding:5rem 5vw}
  .about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:2.5rem}
  .about-img-wrap{max-height:380px;overflow:hidden}
  .about-img{object-fit:cover;object-position:center top}
  .about-h2{font-size:1.7rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
  .fact-block{padding:1.2rem 1.3rem}
  .about-quote{font-size:1.3rem}

  /* NOT TEACHING */
  #notteaching{padding:5rem 5vw}
  .not-item{font-size:1.1rem}
  .yes-main{font-size:2.2rem}

  /* REGISTER */
  #register{padding:5rem 5vw}
  .register-h2{font-size:2rem}
  .register-details{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
  .register-detail{padding:1.5rem 1rem}
  .rd-value{font-size:0.95rem}
  .reg-form{max-width:100%}
  .btn-register{font-size:1rem;padding:1.2rem}

  /* CTA */
  #cta{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .cta-img-wrap{min-height:280px}
  .cta-right{padding:4rem 5vw}
  .cta-h2{font-size:1.6rem}

  /* FOOTER */
  footer{flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;text-align:center;padding:2rem 5vw}

  /* FLOATING BAR */
  .float-bar{padding:0.8rem 4vw}
  .float-bar-info{gap:0.6rem}
  .float-bar-detail:nth-child(5){display:none}
  .float-bar-value{font-size:0.78rem}
  .float-bar-price{font-size:1.1rem}
  .float-bar-sep{height:26px}
  .float-bar .btn-gold{padding:0.65rem 1.2rem;font-size:0.82rem;animation:none;opacity:1}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="אידית קליימן" class="nav-logo">
  <a href="#register" class="nav-btn">להרשמה לסדנה</a>
</nav>

<section id="hero">
  <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="" class="hero-img">
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="אידית קליימן" class="hero-logo-img">
    <h1 class="hero-h1">
      את מדהימה. באמת.<br><span>אבל מותר לך לרצות יותר.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      עשית הכול נכון. קריירה, הישגים, תנועה קדימה.<br>אבל משהו בפנים כבר לא יושב במקום.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-details">
      <div class="hero-detail">
        <span class="hero-detail-label">תאריך</span>
        <span class="hero-detail-val">27.5.26</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-detail">
        <span class="hero-detail-label">שעות</span>
        <span class="hero-detail-val">17:30 - 21:30</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-detail">
        <span class="hero-detail-label">מיקום</span>
        <span class="hero-detail-val">הוד השרון</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-detail">
        <span class="hero-detail-label">עלות</span>
        <span class="hero-detail-val">189 &#8362;</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="#register" class="btn-gold">אני נרשמת לסדנה</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="opener">
  <div class="opener-inner">
    <p class="opener-pre reveal">
      זה שהגעת לפה -<br>כנראה ראית משהו שנגע בך.
    </p>
    <h2 class="opener-main reveal">
      יש דברים שלמדת להיות<br>כדי לשרוד, כדי להצליח, <span>כדי להגיע רחוק.</span><br>והם באמת הביאו אותך רחוק.<br>אבל עכשיו - יש משהו שעוצר אותך.
    </h2>
    <p class="opener-sub reveal">
      זה לא עייפות. זה לא חולשה.<br>
      זה קוד ישן שנכתב בילדות - ועדיין מנהל אותך היום.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="pain">
  <div class="pain-inner">
    <div class="pain-header reveal">
      <span class="sec-label">אם זה מוכר</span>
      <h2 class="sec-h2">את לא <span>לבד.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-grid">
      <div class="pain-card reveal">
        <div class="pain-card-title">מרגישה תקועה</div>
        <div class="pain-card-body">עובדת קשה, מגיעה להישגים - ובכל זאת משהו לא מרגיש מספיק.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card reveal">
        <div class="pain-card-title">על אוטומט</div>
        <div class="pain-card-body">מגיבה כמו שתמיד הגבת, גם כשאת יודעת שכדאי אחרת.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card reveal">
        <div class="pain-card-title">מחזיקה הכול</div>
        <div class="pain-card-body">את מנהלת את כולם - אבל מי מחזיקה אותך?</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card reveal">
        <div class="pain-card-title">חוסר שקט פנימי</div>
        <div class="pain-card-body">הצלחת מבחוץ, אבל בפנים עדיין מחכה לאישור שלא בא.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="workshop">
  <div class="workshop-inner">
    <div class="workshop-header reveal">
      <span class="sec-label">קוד פתוח - הסדנה</span>
      <h2 class="sec-h2">ארבעה שלבים.<br><span>סיפור אחד - שלך.</span></h2>
      <p>הסדנה לא תלמד אותך להיות סופרוומן. את כבר כזאת.<br>היא תלמד אותך להפסיק לרוץ על קוד שלא כתבת.</p>
